Total number of events with dimension categorized by the communities as Intellectual, scheduled between [...date...] and [...date...], activities that are mentally stimulating or creative in nature to promote alert and interested minds

JP_Physical
Total number of events with dimension categorized by the communities as Physical, scheduled between [...date...] and [...date...], activities that promote improved health and physical functional ability

JP_Purposeful
Total number of events with dimenstion categorized by the communities as Purposeful, scheduled between [...date...] and [...date...], activities that celebrate residents' previous professional/volunteer skills to contribute to their community and/or mentor others

JP_Social
Total number of events with dimension categorized by the communities as Social, scheduled between [...date...] and [...date...], activities that encourage personal connections with others through conversation and interactive activities; includes intergenerational connectedness

JP_Spiritual
Total number of events with dimension categorized by the communities as Spiritual, scheduled between [...date...] and [...date...], activities that promote meaning and purpose in life, guided by personal values. These include faith-based activities, meditation, mindful excercise & experiencing nature

JP_Environmental
Total number of events with dimension categorized by the communities as Environmental, scheduled between [...date...] and [...date...], activities that promote respect for and enjoyment of natural resources; oppotunity to bring nature into our everyday lives

JP_Other
Total number of events with dimension categorized by the communities as Other, scheduled between [...date...] and [...date...]

Total number of events offered between [...date...] and [...date...]

JP_Unique Check-ins
Total number of unique residents attending an event between [...date...] and [...date...]. If one resident attended yoga 5 times in this timeframe, the count would be 1

JP_Residents
Total number of residents who have an active status at some point between [...date...] and [...date...]
